Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.16,0:00:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被染黑的小鳥羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓那個和黃泉很像的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也無法飛翔了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(630,500)\an1\pos(96,573)\fs40\bord2\be2}第六話\N那個時候不可能存在的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:03:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 真綯 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 Black★Rock Shooter…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.56,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.58,0:05:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳都幹了什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過給少女們施加最大的身心負擔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個世界的少女們就能消除僅存的人性
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的力量就會覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給小鳥遊同學施加負擔讓她作為Deadmaster覺醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳…讓Black★Rock Shooter…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到真綯居然會被吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想如果真綯能接觸到那個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而使Black★Rock Shooter覺醒的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black★Rock Shooter會毀掉那個世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那樣的話 妳知道我們的那孩子會怎麼樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這樣下去的話 大家都很難受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.35,0:06:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 只要在這裡殺掉黑衣同學的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…下得了手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學明明是無辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能真的下手啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學被囚禁在Black★Rock Shooter的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試著呼喚一下Black★Rock Shooter體內的黑衣同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有誰的聲音能傳達給她的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳要記住我最想保護的不是黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我們的那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}好難受×N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學 求妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快聽見我的…聲音吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑衣同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…傳達到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…和那孩子相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那孩子的開端始於那個夏日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.62,0:09:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…妳怎麼了啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.54,0:09:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 有沒有冰淇淋啊 冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 那是3丁目神足家的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 妳認識？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很有名嗎 因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是在學校還是在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.46,0:10:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇都留下了我完全無法想像的痛苦回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 她也默默忍受著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的痛楚都塞進纖細的身軀之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道為什麼總覺得無法放任她不管
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇好堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅強？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真羨慕妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種人總是為一些瑣碎小事而焦頭爛額
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.44,0:11:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的很厲害 我很尊敬妳喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是有另一個女孩在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人欺負 或者感到傷心的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.76,0:11:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是由宇的另一個女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承受所有痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 由宇並不覺得有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放任這孩子孤單一人…我這麼想到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能為由宇做點什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一點也好 如果我能理解由宇的傷痛的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 這不是麥茶 是掛麵的澆汁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙耶 由宇的家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁那樣想到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由宇幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.57,0:13:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由宇在向折磨她的一切復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在想這是我幹的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.71,0:13:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.46,0:14:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火災的原因是由宇繼父忘記摁滅的煙頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個笑容…我一直無法忘懷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做我才能補償由宇呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.88,0:14:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我一直很想成為由宇的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.09,0:15:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳肯原諒我的話 無論什麼我都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得比這個世界還要痛苦的世界…哪裡都不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次妳又在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做什麼奇怪的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我討厭痛楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我在想要不要讓那個孩子承受這份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐…呐 由宇妳怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我 無論什麼妳都願意做對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚自己的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？沙耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 是另一個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Black Gold Saw
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.35,0:17:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快清醒過來吧 黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.93,0:18:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.47,0:19:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子保護了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明對那孩子做了很過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 小沙耶得到原諒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不得不保護的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明必須得保護那個世界才行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.09,0:19:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關係啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 小沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在一定很難受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 Black★Rock Shooter
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把自己的願望強加在妳們身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好難受 我…終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止我都把這份痛楚強行推到了別人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個自己總是在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背負著我們的苦惱和混亂不堪的思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 透過那些戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.13,0:21:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過另一個自己的死亡而消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔚藍眼睛的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算傷害他人也要繼續戰鬥的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了從苦惱中解救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:15.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:20.41,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.82,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かのようになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:27.82,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要變得和某人一樣堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.79,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけどなれるはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.79,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又明白無法實現這個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.59,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いじけるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.59,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果為此垂頭喪氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:43.85,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心の中にいるもう一人の自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:43.85,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}存在於心中的另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:49.32,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}教えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:49.32,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}會告訴我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:57.40,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あるがままなんかじゃきっといられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:57.40,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一成不變畏縮不前的話一定會被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:21:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明白是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:04.13,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もがみんな悩んでもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:22:04.13,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論是誰 大家都背負著苦惱而掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得很不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:11.22,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}弱音吐いたり 愚痴ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:11.22,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}偶爾示弱 偶爾牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:18.18,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そうやって毎日を過ごしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:18.18,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就像這樣度過了每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:24.94,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}傷つけられることに慣れた僕らは知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:24.94,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於習慣受傷的我們已然知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:31.77,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}優しさとか思いだけじゃ生きて行けないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.37,0:22:31.77,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只靠溫柔的願望無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:38.13,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど自分らしくありたいと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:38.13,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但是希望可以保持自我的本色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HE2DCD3&\fs32\fr-15\frx25\pos(602,373)}資料夾已刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:46.50,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつだって 僕ら歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:46.50,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論何時 我們都會一路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事 絕對不對啊
